    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔表示，商业房地产风险“可能持续数年”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/fed-s-powell-says-cre-to-be-a-risk-probably-for-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在美国参议院银行和住房委员会半年一度的证词中评论银行面临的商业房地产风险时表示：“这种风险一直存在，而且会伴随我们一段时间，可能持续数年。” （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/fed-s-powell-says-cre-to-be-a-risk-probably-for-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:38:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特警告 G-7 禁止俄罗斯扣押其资产，并威胁出售其债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/saudi-arabia-veiled-threat-to-g7-over-russia-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，沙特阿拉伯今年早些时候曾私下暗示，如果七国集团决定扣押俄罗斯近 3000 亿美元的冻结资产，沙特阿拉伯可能会出售部分欧洲债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/saudi-arabia-veiled-threat-to-g7-over-russia-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 13:28:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>制裁风险导致俄罗斯接受人民币步伐放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/russia-s-embrace-of-chinese-yuan-stalls-over-risk-from-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受俄罗斯入侵乌克兰与西方国家关系紧张的影响，俄罗斯总统普京的战时经济中人民币的快速增长或许已经达到极限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/russia-s-embrace-of-chinese-yuan-stalls-over-risk-from-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 06:38:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
